Using mac address , find location of anybody

First you need to find mac address of that person.

sudo curl -i -s -k -X 'POST' -H 'User-Agent: Dalvik/2.1.0 (Linux; U; Android 5.0.1; Nexus 5 Build/LRX22C)' -H 'Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded' \ 'http://mobile.maps.yandex.net/cellid_location/?clid=1866854&lac=-1&cellid=-1&operatorid=null&countrycode=null&signalstrength=-1&wifinetworks=000000000000:-65&app=ymetro'


Note : Mac address is crucial and should not be shared, reason being could be easily spoofed and let you be in trouble. 
